                                </g>
                            </svg>
                            Whatsapp:
                            <a class=" text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-700 dark:hover:text-gray-200 dark:focus:outline-none dark:focus:ring-1 dark:focus:ring-gray-600" href="https://wa.me/919911574941">919911574941</a>   
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="gap-2 flex flex-col border p-8 rounded-lg border-gray-200">
                        <h3 class="font-semibold text-xl text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">Email</h3>
                        <p class="font-medium inline-flex gap-x-2 text-gray-700">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-800 dark:text-white" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 20 16">
                                <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="m19 2-8.4 7.05a1 1 0 0 1-1.2 0L1 2m18 0a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H2a1 1 0 0 0-1 1m18 0v12a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H2a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V2"/>
                            </svg>
                            Sales:
                            <a class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-700 dark:hover:text-gray-200 dark:focus:outline-none dark:focus:ring-1 dark:focus:ring-gray-600" href="mailto: info@jainhydraulics.com">info@jainhydraulics.com</a>
                        </p>
                        <p class="font-medium inline-flex gap-x-2 text-gray-700">
                            <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gray-800 dark:text-white" aria-hidden="true" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 20 16">
                                <path stroke="currentColor" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="m19 2-8.4 7.05a1 1 0 0 1-1.2 0L1 2m18 0a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H2a1 1 0 0 0-1 1m18 0v12a1 1 0 0 1-1 1H2a1 1 0 0 1-1-1V2"/>
                            </svg>
                            Support:
                            <a class="text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-700 dark:hover:text-gray-200 dark:focus:outline-none dark:focus:ring-1 dark:focus:ring-gray-600" href="mailto: support@jainhydraulics.com">support@jainhydraulics.com</a>                     
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="order-1">
                <ContactsForm text="Contact Us" innerText="We'd love to talk about how we can help you. " />
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>